Package: nifffty
Title: Post Events to IFTTT 'Maker' Channels and Receive 'Maker' Events
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Bob", "Rudis", email = "bob@rudis.net", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides a simple interface to post messages to IFTTT 'Maker' channels
             from R, enabling R scripts to trigger IFTTT recipes with optional data payloads
             and also receive and process Maker web requests.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), methods
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat, Rook, httpuv, jsonlite
Imports: httr
